headline: Southwest baggage fees: 3 ways your bags can still fly for free
summary: Southwest Airlines (LUV) announced that starting May 28, it will no longer offer two free checked bags for every passenger. Yahoo Finance Senior Writer Kendall Little joins Wealth host Brad Smith to share ways you can keep getting your checked bags for free, including through A-list status, business select fares, and having a Southwest credit card.
